articles.title: OpenAI is winding down its GPT-4 AI model in ChatGPT - TechCrunch
articles.description: OpenAI will soon retire GPT-4, an AI model it launched over two years ago, from ChatGPT, the company announced in a changelog.
articles.content:
OpenAI will soon retire GPT-4, an AI model it launched over two years ago, from ChatGPT, according to a changelog posted on Thursday.
